## 🛠️ How to Verify

Since external dependencies (like ChromaDB) were updated, please follow these steps to ensure the environment is synced:

### 1. Rebuild & Start Containers
Run this from the project root to ensure the new `bcrypt` and `requirements.txt` are applied:
```powershell
docker-compose up -d --build backend
```

### 2. Run Integration Tests
This script verifies the full flow: Register -> Login -> Streaming Query -> History List.
```powershell
docker-compose exec -e PYTHONPATH=/app backend python -m tests.test_phase4
```

> [!TIP]
> You can also explore the automatically generated API documentation by visiting:
> `http://localhost:8000/docs` (Swagger UI)

